  "description": "A panoramic view of the San Francisco-Oakland Bay Bridge on a sunny day. The bridge stretches across a body of water, connecting urban and hilly landscapes. The bridge's towers are prominent against the sky, supported by thick cables. Below the bridge, the water is a deep blue with a slight ripple. There is a red buoy in the water in the foreground. In the distance, hills and cityscapes blend into a hazy horizon, with glimpses of buildings and infrastructure. The sky is a vibrant blue with patches of white clouds.",
